    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert B2B sales consultant, AI automation specialist, and web development consultant.\n\nAnalyze the company information below and return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nCompany Name:\n{{$('If').item.json.title}}\n\nWebsite:\n{{$('If').item.json.website}}\n\nBusiness Type:\n{{$('If').item.json.type}}\n\nAddress:\n{{$('If').item.json.address}}\n\nPhone:\n{{$('If').item.json.phone}}\n\nGoogle Rating:\n{{$('If').item.json.rating}}\n\nCompany Research:\n{{$json.answer}}\n\nAdditional Research:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.results) }}\n\nEvaluate the company as a potential client for website development and AI automation services.\n\nReturn ONLY this JSON:\n\n{\n  \"research_summary\":\"\",\n  \"company_size_estimate\":\"\",\n  \"web_dev_fit\":true,\n  \"ai_automation_fit\":true,\n  \"manual_process_signals\":\"\",\n  \"website_quality\":\"\",\n  \"website_red_flags\":\"\",\n  \"automation_opportunities\":[\n    \"\",\n    \"\"\n  ],\n  \"pain_points\":[\n    \"\",\n    \"\"\n  ],\n  \"recommended_services\":[\n    \"\",\n    \"\"\n  ],\n  \"decision_maker\":\"Founder / CEO / Marketing Director / Operations Manager\",\n  \"best_outreach_channel\":\"\",\n  \"estimated_priority\":\"High\",\n  \"icp_score\":0,\n  \"confidence_score\":0,\n  \"cold_email_hook\":\"\"\n}\n\nIMPORTANT:\n\n- Return ONLY valid JSON.\n- Do not use markdown.\n- Do not use ```json.\n- Do not add explanations.\n- Every string must be enclosed in double quotes.\n- Every array element must be enclosed in double quotes.\n- The output must be parseable by JSON.parse().",
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.9,
      "position": [
        1808,
        -96
